    http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0

    ValueWithAttributes TimeSpan

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:TimeSpan

      • Description

        Specifies the arrival date and departure date which covers the whole Reservation.

    • Example XML

      <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>

<TimeSpan end="12/20/2016" start="2010-12-31T11:55:00Z" xmlns="http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0"/>

      Example JSON

      {
  "TimeSpan" : {
    "value" : null,
    "start" : "2010-12-31T11:55:00Z",
    "end" : "12/20/2016"
  }
}

      • Attribute Summary

        Attributes 
        Name Description
        start
        Specifies the start date for the booking as a whole.
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:DateTime
        Example Value 2010-12-31T11:55:00Z
        Required true
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        end
        Specifies the end date for the booking as a whole.
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:DateTime
        Example Value 12/20/2016
        Required true
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
